Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:37.90,ED-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}わが師の恩
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.01,0:14:32.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}于校庭受教
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.48,0:14:37.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}师恩比天高
